# View-snapshot compare debris (AN-005): a failing `assertViewSnapshot` writes
# `<name>.actual.txt` next to the doc/test for eyeballing the mismatch. It is a
# throwaway diff artifact — never a committed reference — so ignore it everywhere
# to keep it out of `git add` by accident.
